book.title: Stones Unturned (The Menagerie #3)
book.description: Storyline: Stones Unturned (The Menagerie #3) The Menagerie at the edge of the abyss. A powerful, demonic force seeks Danny Ferrick, a changeling and the youngest member of the Menagerie. Now Doyle's team must race to save their friend from falling into the darkness-and taking all of humanity with him.
book.author: Christopher Golden
